  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/22280fbcbdc0b004192079409699fa72.avif?t=1693272868\" width=610 height=120 /></span><br>For too long have animals been defenseless on the road.<br><br>Now they're fighting back..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/2dc17221a1b307a08cbfe2e01c7ee794.poster.avif?t=1693272868\" width=482 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/2dc17221a1b307a08cbfe2e01c7ee794.webm?t=1693272868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/2dc17221a1b307a08cbfe2e01c7ee794.mp4?t=1693272868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/c7a5fac3af7c45964f9a267c9785b5c6.avif?t=1693272868\" width=610 height=120 /></span><br>There are 4 different hazards, each with their own effect. Drop them on the road to make the cars crash!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/9c06b89a00837ffdeace7e071d4a2f29.poster.avif?t=1693272868\" width=278 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/9c06b89a00837ffdeace7e071d4a2f29.webm?t=1693272868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/9c06b89a00837ffdeace7e071d4a2f29.mp4?t=1693272868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/949588ff11185fd328d3a29e1be70e1c.poster.avif?t=1693272868\" width=278 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/949588ff11185fd328d3a29e1be70e1c.webm?t=1693272868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/949588ff11185fd328d3a29e1be70e1c.mp4?t=1693272868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/ab32408c1d8eab5f55429d9929da8107.avif?t=1693272868\" width=610 height=120 /></span><br><strong>Survival</strong> 1 life, cars keep speeding up. How many can you crash before you die?<br><br><strong>Levels</strong> They start easy then get harder. Each has a goal to complete.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/f96c0b739a3962fa6bde93848162977e.poster.avif?t=1693272868\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/f96c0b739a3962fa6bde93848162977e.webm?t=1693272868\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/f96c0b739a3962fa6bde93848162977e.mp4?t=1693272868\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/2f5120c705f443bd25663eef85317a50.poster.avif?t=1693272868\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781580/extras/2f5120c705f443bd25663eef85317